{"sn46.43:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 46.43 ","sn46.43:0.2":"5. Cakkavattivagga ","sn46.43:0.3":"Marasutta ","sn46.43:1.1":"“Marasenappamaddanam vo, bhikkhave, maggam desessami; ","sn46.43:1.2":"tam sunatha. ","sn46.43:1.3":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, marasenappamaddano maggo? ","sn46.43:1.4":"Yadidam—","sn46.43:1.5":"satta bojjhanga. ","sn46.43:1.6":"Katame satta? ","sn46.43:1.7":"Satisambojjhango …pe… upekkhasambojjhango—","sn46.43:1.8":"ayam kho, bhikkhave, marasenappamaddano maggo”ti. ","sn46.43:1.9":"Tatiyam. "}